# GitHub MCP Preference

For GitHub operations, use MCP tools first when available.

## Required behavior

- Prefer GitHub MCP tools for PRs, issues, comments, checks, and release actions.
- Use command-line GitHub tools (`gh`, git remote operations) only when equivalent MCP tools are unavailable or fail.
- When falling back to CLI, state the fallback reason in the user-facing summary.

## Scope

- Applies to PR creation, PR review comments, merge actions, issue workflows, and release asset operations.
